screen_desc: The screenshot displays a social media interface for creating a post. At the top, it shows the time and a user profile with the name "Hendrick Phan." Below the profile, there are options for post visibility (Public), adding an album, and toggling an AI label. The main prompt asks, "What's on your mind?" Below this, there are several options for enhancing the post, including adding a photo/video, tagging people, indicating a feeling/activity, checking in, going live, selecting a background color, and accessing the camera. The layout is clean and user-friendly, designed for easy interaction.
